<normalizedToken originalValue="Anéis">Aneis</normalizedToken>
(MAD11); Ribeira do 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Córrego">Corrego</normalizedToken>
do Arrochete (MAD30); Ribeira de 
<normalizedToken originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Jorge (MAD37).
</paragraph>
